          <title>Jennings throws for 278 yards to lead SMU to 24-19 Holiday Bowl win over No. 21 Arizona</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Kevin Jennings threw for 278 yards, highlighted by an 80-yard completion on a razzle-dazzle play on the second play from scrimmage, and SMU beat No. 21 Arizona 24-19 in the Holiday Bowl on Friday night.]]></description>
